      <section eId="sec_40_1_116">
        <num>40-1-116</num>
        <content>
          <p>No subdivision of this state, including cities, townships, or counties, shall levy any excise, license, or occupation tax of any nature, on the right of a motor carrier to operate equipment, or on the equipment, or on any incidents of the business of a motor carrier.</p>
